Name: Diffa
Author: Ackara
Summary: Diffa is a **.netstandard** unit-test assertion library that allows you to verify your test results against approved files.
ReleaseNotes:
Version 0.0.9
-------------
Features:
	* Compare any object
	* Compare two files
	* Supports Beyond compare 4
	* Supports Visual Studio diff tool
Tags: approval test unit-testing diff compare approvals verify testing
